        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Kings 5:13",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). On the obstacle which prevented it, \"because of the war, with which they (the enemies) had surrounded me,\" see at ",
        "children": []
